班克斯一周内的第五件新艺术作品出现在沃尔瑟姆斯托的一家炸鱼薯条店外https://www.nme.com/news/banksys-fifth-new-artwork-in-a-week-appears-outside-a-walthamstow-fish-and-chip-shop-3782589?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=班克斯一周内第五件新艺术品出现在沃尔瑟姆斯托炸鱼薯条店外Laura MolloySat, 10 Aug 2024 08:05:48 +0000News https://www.nme.com/?p=3782589 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Banksy-mural.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="班克斯壁画。图片来源：马修·贝克/盖蒂图片社" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Banksy-mural.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Banksy-mural.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Banksy-mural.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Banksy-mural.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Banksy-mural.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Banksy-mural.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>沃尔瑟姆斯托的新壁画是在本周早些时候佩卡姆的第四幅壁画被盗之后绘制的</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/banksys-fifth-new-artwork-in-a-week-appears-outside-a-walthamstow-fish-and-chip-shop-3782589">班克斯一周内第五件新艺术作品出现在沃尔瑟姆斯托一家炸鱼薯条店外的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Banksy-mural.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="班克斯壁画。图片来源：马修·贝克/盖蒂图片社" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Banksy-mural.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Banksy-mural.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Banksy-mural.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Banksy-mural.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Banksy-mural.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Banksy-mural.-Credit_-Matthew-Baker_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/banksy">班克斯的</a>另一件新作品已在伦敦亮相。看看下面。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/idles-glastonbury-2024-other-stage-review-setlist-photos-3769997">2024 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节闲逛：班克斯协助的抗议活动甚至消除了极高的期望</a></strong></li></ul><p>昨天（8月9日）班克斯在伦敦东北部沃尔瑟姆斯托的一家炸鱼薯条店上方分享了他本周的第五件作品。这幅壁画描绘了两只正在吃鱼的鹈鹕，下午艺术家在他的 Instagram 上认领了这幅壁画。</p><p>在班克斯确认这件作品是他的作品之前，沃尔瑟姆斯托的议员斯特拉·克里西<a href="https://www.facebook.com/reel/1893693144440020" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在 Facebook 上对这件新艺术品做出了反应</a>，说道：“沃尔瑟姆斯托。就连我们的薯片也比其他人的要酷一点。即使这不是 #banksy，它也很精彩，而且里面的筹码也很神奇，所以感谢今天为我们的街头艺术添加这种魔力的人。”</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/banksys-new-wolf-street-art-stolen-from-peckham-3782133">周四，这位艺术家的第四件作品在佩卡姆被盗</a>。这幅艺术作品描绘了一只狼对着月亮嚎叫，画在 Rye Lane 一家店面顶上的卫星天线上，紧邻 UCKG 帮助中心。</p><p>该作品曝光后不久，一群穿着黑色连帽衫、戴着口罩和手套的男子似乎爬上了大楼，拆除了卫星天线，并将其从原来的位置偷走了。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C-csjTiMN2R/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: